FBIS4-62220 "drsov093_b_94016" FBIS-SOV-94-093 Daily Report 12 May 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Several Arrested for Murder Several Arrested for Murder LD1205205894 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel Network in Russian 2009 GMT 12 May 94 LD1205205894 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel Network Russian BFN [From the "Novosti" newscast] [Text] Several people have been arrested in connection with the investigation of the murder of Andrey Ayzderdzis, deputy of the State Duma. Vladimir Kolesnikov, head of the main directorate of the criminal investigation department of the Russian Interior Ministry, announced this to journalists in Moscow on Thursday. We can state that we know who committed the crime, he said; however, the cause of the crime is not yet entirely clear.
